{"tid":1991100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］尚德停車場圍白布及鐵板裝修　","createTime":"2020-04-27T08:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T13:34:01.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"10974dc25d37777a1e0ae8005b1c5f2f8b1dec34","tid":1991100,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:06:22.000Z","msg":"周梓樂二樓祭壇圍白布裝修　牆上噴漆被清<br />\n<br />\n去年科大學生周梓樂及知專學生陳彥霖離世，市民在將軍澳尚德停車場設祭壇悼念，連月來祭壇已多次被清拆、破壞。<br />\n<br />\n記者今日發現，至於停車場二樓周梓樂墮樓位置的祭壇，全層都已圍上白布，有工人油走牆上的噴漆。<br />\n<br />\n另外，停車場外地面的祭壇亦被大型鐵板及雪糕筒圍封，有工人表示是受領展指派到場施工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5rxsDp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5rxsDp.jpg&h=83c852fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"852b773d2dc5a4736f98c0602be7804440d5be4d","tid":1991100,"uid":3480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"整走左就當無事發生咩傻鳩"},{"pid":"5d4d13285a60a74b99f0b55a856e2d936587210d","tid":1991100,"uid":5490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"佢成個停車場拆左佢都無用架，一樣可能照係街悼念，除非佢成條村封左佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582cf597894b3a55239829304f7d63e1997733b9","tid":1991100,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:08:48.000Z","msg":"大畫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dd0b15997b71037c11808da859a24a6a4be519","tid":1991100,"uid":66049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"支那式思維"},{"pid":"297c2deae6c56cb758dc30e440cf9a79902bbfe9","tid":1991100,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"有油漆有天拿水又唔掛好電線好危險好易著火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aa167de657f06bab70653ac07cc75105507529","tid":1991100,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09: